project_descr: This project will extend the institutional strengthening support for two additional years from January 2015 to December 2016 for the national Ozone Layer Protection Unit, Department of Environment of the Government of Islamic Republic of Iran.

outputs.output_descr: This project will extend the institutional strengthening support for two additional years from April 2015 to March 2017 for the national Ozone Layer Protection Unit, Department of Environment of the Government of Islamic Republic of Iran.
